text[0] = "@A bee I am..."
text[1] = "@...not..."
text[2] = "@I am no mere bee."
text[3] = "@I've come here from ten years in the future..."
text[4] = "@...and in the future, all is devastation and ruin..."
text[5] = "@The universal cosmic destroyer known as Giygas sent all to the horror of eternal darkness."
text[6] = "@However, I implore you to listen."
text[7] = "@In my era, a prophecy has been handed down from the times of old."
text[8] = "@It is prophesied that, \"When the chosen boy reaches the point, he will find the light."
text[9] = "@The passing of time will shatter the rock of nightmares and reveal the path of light.\""
text[10] = "@Ah, you must be wondering what I am referring to, is that right, Ness?"
text[11] = "@What?"
text[12] = "@You seem surprised that I know your name."
text[13] = "@Well, it is my strong belief, Ness, that you are this chosen boy."
text[14] = "@Yes..."
text[15] = "@Giygas must have set his monstrous plans in motion somewhere on Earth..."
text[16] = "@If you begin to confront the fiend posthaste,"
text[17] = "@you may have time to counter Giygas's evil intentions."
text[18] = "@You must remember three significant virtues on your adventure."
text[19] = "@They are: {pause}Wisdom. {pause}Courage. {pause}Friendship."
text[20] = "@The legends from ancient days speak of three boys and one girl who band together and bring an end to Giygas and his plans."
text[21] = "@I will reveal more later."
text[22] = "@Go now, and do not cling to uncertainty about the future."
text[23] = "@You have much work to do, Ness."
text[24] = "@newbox:Buzz Buzz"
text[25] = "@Do you understand?\n%n"
text[26] = "@prompt:3&Yes%No"